### ========== USERS (via bigbank → user-service) ==========

### Créer un customer
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Jean",
  "lastname": "Mirabeau",
  "email": "jean@bigbank.com",
  "phone": "0645324567",
  "password": "Motdepasse123"
}

### Créer un 2ème customer
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Marie",
  "lastname": "Madeleine",
  "email": "marie@bigbank.com",
  "password": "autrepassword1"
}

### Créer un employee (directement sur user-service)
POST http://localhost:3004/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Admin",
  "lastname": "Dupont",
  "email": "admin@bigbank.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123",
  "role": "employee"
}

### Lister les users via bigbank (customers uniquement)
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### Lister TOUS les users (via user-service)
GET http://localhost:3004/users

### Filtrer : uniquement les customers
GET http://localhost:3004/users?role=customer

### Filtrer : uniquement les employees
GET http://localhost:3004/users?role=employee

### Récupérer un utilisateur
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1

### Modifier le téléphone
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "0634214321"
}

### Tester email en doublon (doit renvoyer 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Doublon",
  "lastname": "Test",
  "email": "jean@bigbank.com",
  "password": "Motdepasse123"
}

### Tester validation (doit renvoyer 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "",
  "email": "pasunemail",
  "password": "court"
}

### Supprimer un utilisateur
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/1

### ========== ACCOUNTS (via bigbank → account-service) ==========

### Créer un compte courant pour le user 1
POST http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Compte courant",
  "type": "checking"
}

### Créer un compte épargne pour le user 1
POST http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Épargne",
  "type": "savings"
}

### Lister les comptes du user 1
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts

### Détail du compte 1
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts/1

### Modifier le label du compte
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Compte principal"
}

### Supprimer un compte
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts/2

### ========== TRANSACTIONS ==========

### Créer un transfert (du compte 1 vers le compte 2)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 15,
  "description": "Virement vers épargne"
}

### Lister toutes les transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions

### Transactions d'un compte spécifique
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/account/1

### Vérifier les soldes après transfert
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts

### ========== PAGINATION ==========

### Users page 1, limit 2
GET http://localhost:3000/users?page=1&limit=2

### Users page 2, limit 2
GET http://localhost:3000/users?page=2&limit=2

### Transactions paginées
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?page=1&limit=5

### ========== ADMIN (port 3001) ==========

### Vue admin complète (users + comptes + transactions)
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/overview

### Admin - tous les users
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/users

### Admin - user avec ses comptes
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/users/1

### Admin - toutes les transactions
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/transactions

### ===== LOAD BALANCER Ex-3 : tous les LB via bigbank-lb :3030 =====

### USERS (bigbank-lb → bigbank-1/2 → user-lb → user-svc-1/2)

### Créer un utilisateur
POST http://localhost:3030/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Alice",
  "lastname": "Dupont",
  "email": "alice@test.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### Lister les utilisateurs
GET http://localhost:3030/users

### Voir un utilisateur
GET http://localhost:3030/users/1

### COMPTES (bigbank-lb → account-lb → account-svc-1/2 → PostgreSQL)

### Créer un compte courant
POST http://localhost:3030/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Compte Courant",
  "type": "checking"
}

### Créer un compte épargne
POST http://localhost:3030/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Épargne",
  "type": "savings"
}

### Lister les comptes
GET http://localhost:3030/users/1/accounts

### --- TRANSACTIONS (bigbank-lb → transaction-svc → account-lb + notification) ---

### Virement de 25€
POST http://localhost:3030/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 25,
  "description": "Test Load Balancer Ex-3"
}

### Vérifier les soldes (75€ et 125€)
GET http://localhost:3030/users/1/accounts

### Lister les transactions
GET http://localhost:3030/transactions

### ADMIN (bigbank-admin → user-lb + account-lb + transaction-svc)

### Vue d'ensemble
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/overview

### Users admin
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/users

### Transactions admin
GET http://localhost:3001/admin/transactions

### TEST DIRECT DES LB (pour vérifier qu'ils répondent)

### user-lb direct
GET http://localhost:3010/users

### account-lb direct
GET http://localhost:3020/accounts/user/1

### bigbank-lb direct
GET http://localhost:3030/users
